      <title>美国将派代表团出席台湾下任总统就职典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/us-to-send-delegation-to-inauguration-of-taiwan-s-next-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国将派出一个由前政府官员组成的代表团前往台湾参加当选总统赖清德的就职典礼，称此次访问符合长期以来的惯例，旨在控制这个自治岛屿与中国之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/us-to-send-delegation-to-inauguration-of-taiwan-s-next-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果要求国际社会对卢旺达矿产出口实施禁运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/congo-demands-international-embargo-on-rwandan-mineral-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国呼吁对邻国卢旺达的金属出口实施国际禁运，并指责卢旺达政府利用叛乱组织窃取其自然资源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/congo-demands-international-embargo-on-rwandan-mineral-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:40:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
